# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# KIMatrix Web - Frontend Environment Variables
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and configure with your values
# NEVER commit .env.local, .env.development.local, or .env.production.local
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PUBLIC ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (Exposed to Browser)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are prefixed with NEXT_PUBLIC_ and accessible in client-side code
# via process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_*
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Backend API Base URL
# Development: http://localhost:5000
# Production: https://api.kimatrix.com (replace with your domain)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000

# App Version (optional, for display in UI)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_VERSION=1.0.0

# Feature Flags (optional)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_PWA=true
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SERVER-ONLY ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (NOT Exposed to Browser)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are only available in server-side code (API routes, getServerSideProps)
# DO NOT prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC_
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Future: Add server-only secrets here when needed
# Example: Internal API keys, database connections for server components, etc.

# INTERNAL_API_KEY=your-internal-api-key-here
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/dbname

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEPLOYMENT ENVIRONMENT
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Automatically set by Next.js based on npm script (dev/build/start)
# NODE_ENV=development | production | test

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTES
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create .env.local for local development (git-ignored)
# 2. Create .env.production.local for production builds (git-ignored)
# 3. NEVER commit files containing real values (.env.local, etc.)
# 4. For Vercel/Netlify, set variables in the platform dashboard
# 5. Public env vars are embedded at BUILD TIME, not runtime
# 6. Changing public env vars requires rebuild: npm run build
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
